title: 2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 03)
description:
-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Romans 12:10 - "Be devoted to one another in love.  Honor one another above yourselves."

This third bundle of 2014 is being torrented today in honor and support of the following 17 people who took a moment to comment in my first two threads of 2014.  They are (1) BlessedMom, (2) holyflow, (3) iDivine, (4) jw360, (5) kbb81tn, (6) kevkev933, (7) Marvado, (8) mutsoo, (9) Nathan.S, (10) PaleoPirate, (11) Phaedron, (12) super1313, (13) Thighmstr, (14) tweakedboy, (15) ua-pupsik, (16) WarcraftAddict, and (17) Wheezin.

Thank you all.

ROCK: A Jesus Church, Anthem Lights, Brad And Rebekah, Kutless.  HARDCORE/METAL: A Sight To See, Hundredth, Pantokrator.  ALTERNATIVE: A Smith, The Duskwhales, Manchester Orchestra.  HIP-HOP/RAP: Andy Mineo, Caleb McCoy, J-Heir, Joey Prophet, Josh G Massey, NMG Productions, Q.  PRAISE & WORSHIP: Angela Christine, Doug Matlock, Gillum Rose, Josh Baldwin, Sojourn Worship, Various.  INSTRUMENTAL: Blue Sky Perch.  CONTEMPORARY: City Harbor, Evan Craft, Jacques Guidry, John Mark McMillan, Joy Lewis.  ELECTRONIC: DJ I Rock Jesus.  INDIE: Francisco Road, Trembling Hearts.  ACOUSTIC: Housefires.  SINGER-SONGWRITER: Hurricane Irene, Kyle Cooke.  POP: Michael Paynter, The Obb, Red Roots.  REGGAE: Papa San.
